                "Sailer"
            ]
        ]
    ],
    "At the Museum, he curated several major exhibitions, including <em>African Art in the Cycle of Life</em> (1987) with Roslyn Walker, the inaugural exhibition of the museum's site on the Mall.": [],
    "Sieber authored the introduction to <em>Selected Works from the Collection of the National Museum of African Art</em> and <em>Hair in African Art and Culture</em> and the essay in \"Extreme Canvas: Hand-Painted Movie Posters From Ghana.\"": [
